SOL(1)
======
Jason Lingle <jasonlingle@yahoo.com>

NAME
----
sol(iloquy) --- The programmers' editor of your nightmares

SYNOPSIS
--------
sol [*OPTIONS*] [*file* [...]]

DESCRIPTION
-----------
Introduction
~~~~~~~~~~~~
Soliloquy will be a highly extensible, non-visual editor with modern features,
which will include:

- Automatic indentation
- Automatic word-wrap
- Syntax highlighting
- Fast line editing
- Multiple buffers
- Infinite undo
